parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down
and the ABS and brake warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the DC-DC converter can cause sudden loss of power, loss of braking, and loss of safety critical functions, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The car suddenly loses power during freeway driving
the brake system appears compromised
and the vehicle requires turning off 12V accessories to restore functionality.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the charging system can cause electrocution hazards, damage to the onboard charger, and inability to charge the vehicle.
symptoms: Sparks and electricity were felt when plugging in the J1772 plug
and the charging system no longer charges the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause loss of power, inability to drive the vehicle, and safety issues related to airbag deployment.
symptoms: The battery charged to 55 miles
but dropped to 39 miles while showing 9 bars
and the range drops significantly while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause airbags not to deploy in an accident, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light is on continuously
the airbag system light blinks continuously
and the passenger seat occupancy sensor is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause strange noises, loss of braking, and inability to start the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle won't start
even with a fully charged battery
and there are unusual electrical issues
such as only one window rolling down and doors temporarily locking and refusing to unlock.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the charging station can cause fire hazards, damage to the vehicle, and inability to charge the vehicle.
symptoms: Smoke was coming from the charging port
and the connection had gotten hot enough to melt the plastic and create smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the deployment of airbags without a crash, or the failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash, which can cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is flashing
the passenger airbag light is flashing
the airbag deploys without a crash
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the seatbelt pre-tensioner engages without a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OCS can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deployment of airbags without a crash, or the failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash, which can cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is flashing
the passenger airbag light is flashing
